        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>steak</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature</p><p>Heat a <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pork loin steak[s]</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 1-2 min on each side or until beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1687259959813-x200.jpg",
