    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in a small bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>BBQ glaze</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
